mento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000479.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AR #JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>memoriae\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Vegeiae\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>infelicissimae\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>quae \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> vixit \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> annis\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\u003Cnum value=\"21\">XXI\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>m\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ensibus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"3\">III\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>dieb\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>us\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"17\">XVII\u003C/num> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Par\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\" break=\"no\"/>thenopeus\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\"/>coniugi \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>dulciss\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>imae\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>text of Salinas\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"2\">\u003Cnote>Gualtherus: Vegelae\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"6\">\u003Cnote>Gualtherus: Parthenopeus\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"7-8\">\u003Cnote>Gualtherus: dul-/cissimae\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#AR\">\n                \u003Cp>Alla memoria della sventurata Vegeia che visse ventuno anni tre mesi diciasette giorni. Partenopeo (predispose questo) per l'amatissima coniuge\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#AR\">\n                \u003Cp>In memory of the unfortunate Vegeia who lived twenty-one years three months and seventeen days. Parthenopeus (set this up) for his beloved wife\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>Mommsen follows Gualtherus, the note of (re)discovery by Salinas coming too late for CIL X.2 (but reported in EphEp VIII).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>73\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GIN6NANU\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gualtherus\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1624 [1625]\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>233\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZP8DE8KS\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7198\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"EphEp\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>VIII 695\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/PU8UDAF3\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002649\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"NSA\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Salinas\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Ctitle>NSA\u003C/title>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>567-568\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
